      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-pre-tip-fun      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     pre-tip-fun-999.
       pre-tip-fun-999.
